source.name: FCC Data Collections Under Review (Media Bureau, Wireless Telecommunication Bureau, Wireline Competition Bureau)
source.description: Listing and brief descriptions of various data sets maintained by the Federal Communication Commission provided solely to facilitate public comments on the FCC's data collection, use, and dissemination practices in connection with MB Docket No. [10-XX], WCB Docket No. [10-XX], and WTB Docket No. [10-XX]. These descriptions are not exhaustive and have no interpretive or precedential value.
